#. Tag: para
#: security_ssh.xml:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To generate a client key pair with the default parameters (RSA, 3072 bits), "
"use the <command>ssh-keygen</command> command with no options. Protect your "
"private key with a strong passphrase:"
